<div class="poster">
  <div class="header">
    <h1>Help Shape a Weight Management Intervention for Black Communities</h1>
    <h2>Are you of Black African or Caribbean heritage?</h2>
    <div class="institution">
      Kings College London, Nutritional Sciences<br>
      Life Sciences & Medicine<br>
      Life Course & Population Sciences
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <p>Are you on a journey toward better health and wellness or supporting someone who is? <span class="emphasis">Your voice matters!</span></p>
    <p>I am a PhD researcher at King's College London interested in co-creating an intervention to improve weight management outcomes for Black communities in South London. Your insights and experiences are essential to ensure this intervention is culturally relevant, accessible, and effective.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-title">Why Get Involved?</div>
    <div class="benefit-item"><span>✔</span> <strong>Make a difference</strong> – Help create an intervention that truly meets the needs of Black communities.</div>
    <div class="benefit-item"><span>✔</span> <strong>Share your insights</strong> – Your perspectives will shape the design, accessibility, and effectiveness of the study.</div>
    <div class="benefit-item"><span>✔</span> <strong>Empower your community</strong> – Build trust, address health disparities, and influence real change.</div>
    <div class="benefit-item"><span>✔</span> <strong>Be part of the process</strong> – Co-develop study materials, refine recruitment strategies, and help share findings.</div>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-title">Who Can Join?</div>
    <div class="benefit-item bold-text">Individuals of Black African or Caribbean heritage interested in health and wellness</div>
    <div class="benefit-item">👨‍👩‍👦 Family members, carers (paid or unpaid) supporting loved ones.</div>
    <div class="benefit-item">🏥 Community leaders, patient advocates, and local health professionals.</div>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-title">What Will You Do?</div>
    <div class="benefit-item">💡 Advise on cultural needs and potential barriers.</div>
    <div class="benefit-item">🗣️ Participate in discussions, workshops, and feedback sessions.</div>
    <div class="benefit-item">📝 Help refine study methods, recruitment, and messaging.</div>
    <div class="benefit-item">📢 Co-develop materials and share findings within the community.</div>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-title">Important Details</div>
    <div class="benefit-item">📅 <strong>How Often:</strong> Once a month between April to July – Join virtual or in-person meetings based on group preference.</div>
    <div class="benefit-item">💰 <strong>Compensation:</strong> Paid at £25 per hour + £5 for online meetings (NIHR rate).</div>
    <div class="benefit-item">📍 <strong>Where:</strong> Community spaces, local organisations, and online – Flexible and accessible!</div>
  </div>

